## Limitations

The findings presented in this report are based on available literature and may not encompass all aspects of how social environments influence behavior. Some sources may not be peer-reviewed, and the information is subject to the limitations of the studies cited. Additionally, cultural and individual differences can lead to variations in how social environments impact behavior, which may not be fully captured in the sources reviewed.

